            </div>
           </div>

                 </div>

             </div>
         </form>
        </script>

       <script id="addButtonModal.html" type="text/ng-template">
        <form name="addButton">
         <div class="modal-header">
             <h3 class="modal-title">Add button to page</h3>
         </div>
         <div class="modal-body">
             <div class="form-horizontal">
                 <div class="form-group">
                     <div class="col-lg-2">
                         <label class="control-label" for="buttonText">Text:</label>
                     </div>
                     <div class="col-lg-10">
                         <input type="text" class="form-control" name="buttonText" id="buttonText" placeholder="Text" ng-model="button.Text" required>
                     </div>
                     
                 </div>
                 <div class="form-group">
                     <div class="col-lg-2">
                         <label class="control-label" for="buttonHref">Href:</label>
                     </div>
                         <div class="col-lg-10">
                             <input type="text" class="form-control" name="buttonHref" id="buttonHref" placeholder="Href" ng-model="button.Href" required>
                         </div>
                     </div>
                 <div class="col-lg-2 lg-offset-2">
                     <label class="control-label" for="buttonHrefDS">From DS:</label>
                 </div>
                 <div class="col-lg-8">
                     <input type="text" class="form-control" typeahead-on-select="typeHeadSelected($item)" typeahead="document as document.DocumentName for document in documents | filter:$viewValue | limitTo:8" name="buttonHrefDS" id="buttonHrefDS" placeholder="From document store" ng-model="button.Href" required>
                 </div>
                 <div class ="form-group">
                     
                 </div>
                 <div class="form-group">
                     <div class="col-lg-2">
                         <label class="control-label" for="buttonClass">Class:</label>
                     </div>
                         <div class="col-lg-10">
                             <div class="btn-group">
                                 <button type="button" class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                                     {{button.Class}} <span class="caret"></span>
                                 </button>
                                 <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                                     <li ng-repeat="class in classes">
                                         <a href="" ng-class="class.classDesc" ng-click="button.Class = class.classDesc">{{class.className}}</a>
                                     </li>
                                 </ul>
                             </div>
                         </div>
                     </div>
                 <div class="form-group">
                     <div class="col-lg-2">
                         <label class="control-label" for="buttonTarget">Target:</label>
                     </div>
                         <div class="col-lg-10">
                             <div class="btn-group">
                                 <button type="button" class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                                     {{button.Target}} <span class="caret"></span>
                                 </button>
                                 <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                                     <li ng-repeat="target in targets">
                                         <a href="" ng-click="button.Target = target">{{target}}</a>
                                     </li>
                                 </ul>
                             </div>
                         </div>
                     </div>
                 <div class="form-group">
                     <div class="col-lg-2">
                         <label class="control-label" for="buttonIcon">Icon:</label>
                     </div>
                         <div class="col-lg-10">
                             <div class="btn-group">
                                 <button type="button" class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                                     {{button.Icon}} <span class="caret"></span>
                                 </button>
                                 <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                                     <li ng-repeat="icon in icons">
                                         <a href="" ng-click="button.Icon = icon.className"><i ng-class="icon.className"></i></a>
                                     </li>
                                 </ul>
                             </div>
                         </div>
                     </div>
             </div>
         </div>
         
         <div class="modal-footer">
             <button class="btn btn-success" type="button" ng-disabled="addButton.$invalid" ng-click="ok()">Add</button>
             <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button" ng-click="cancel()">Cancel</button>
         </div>
     </form>
       </script>
